{
  "text": "TMPA is a 3 hourly, 0.25\u00ba \u00d7 0.25\u00ba latitude-longitude resolution gridded product which makes use of the following datasets: the TRMM combined instrument (TCI) data comprising the TRMM Microwave Imager (TMI) and the TRMM precipitation radar used as the source of calibration; microwave (MW) data from several Low Earth Orbit (LEO) satellites; the Climate Prediction Centre (CPC-NOAA) infrared (IR) data and the Global Precipitation Climatology Project (GPCP) gridded monthly rain gauge data [CITATION_1] .",
